<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8036119>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–6. Habitus of Paraphloeostiba: 1—P. conjuncta (holotype), 2—P. coriacea, 3—P. flaveola (holotype), 4—P. gayndahensis (Papua New Guinea), 5—P. papuana (holotype), 6—P. ullrichi (paratype). Scale bars: 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8036119/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8036125>
    dc:description "FIGURES 26–32. Aedeagus and abdominal segments of Paraphloeostiba ullrichi (paratypes): 26—aedeagus (parameral view), 27—aedeagus (lateral view), 28—male tergite VIII (dorsal view), 29—male sternite VIII (ventral view), 30—female tergite VIII (dorsal view), 31—female sternite VIII (ventral view), 32—female genital segment. Scale bar: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8036125/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

